_sText: Well i've been working on this slowly at my friends house everytime i sleepover or something being that my SDK camera is broken. i Finished it up tonight but it's been kinda rushed due to a slight incident in the laundry room (enough said). 25 spawn points for each team. everyone starts out with just a knife but there are grenades on the ground. A rock wall thing seperates the 2 teams at start But there are ways to get passed it. A fair share of secrets on both sides and a little ambience to make it feel a little more real. Expect From the Final Version -Smoothed out and rounder secret cave entrances. -Spawn with a grenade -More grenades on the ground -HDR -Bushes and trees
